{% extends '_templates/base.njk' %}

{% block page_title %}Restaurants{% endblock %}

{% block page_description %} This is where people can find local austin restaurants.{% endblock %}


{% block content %}
<article class="container">
  <h1>Where 2 Eat in Austin</h1>
 <p>Do you need help figuring out where to get a bite?</p>
<p>Don't worry. It's hard visiting a new city and finding the best places to eat at. That is why we created this website. To make things easy for you to make a decision and know what's essential when in Austin. But, in Austin, you can never pick a bad place to eat.</p>
  <div class="row">
    {% for item in atxrestaurants.restaurants %}
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <div class="card mb-4">
      <img src="img/{{ item.image}}" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="card-title text-start">{{item.name}}</h4>
        <h6 class="card-category text-start">{{item.category}}</h6>
        <p class="card-text text-start">{{item.address}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endfor %}
  </div>
{% endblock %}
</article>